## Erlang node name — built dynamically by rel/env.sh.eex
## Format: demo@<wg_ip>  (e.g. demo@10.103.0.1)
-name ${RELEASE_NODE}

## Erlang cookie shared across all cluster instances
## Must be identical on every node (set via RELEASE_COOKIE on Clever Cloud)
-setcookie ${RELEASE_COOKIE}

## Erlang distribution port range (inter-node communication)
-kernel inet_dist_listen_min 9000
-kernel inet_dist_listen_max 9010

## Enable heartbeat watchdog in prod
##-heart
